      "content": "i get the blood test thing but i dont really have time to book an appointment right now and i'm already feeling kinda run down. i've read online that some people do huge doses like this to basically \"reset\" their levels. if i only do it for like 14 days max, isn't the risk of toxicity pretty much zero? it's just a temporary boost.",
